targets.rawSql:
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT(visitor_id)) * ${sample}
FROM "prisme"."events_pageviews"
SAMPLE 1/${sample}
WHERE timestamp >= fromUnixTimestamp(toUnixTimestamp($__fromTime) - (toUnixTimestamp($__toTime) - toUnixTimestamp($__fromTime)))
AND timestamp <= $__fromTime
AND domain IN (${domains:sqlstring})
AND path IN (${pathnames:sqlstring})
AND operating_system IN (${operating_systems:sqlstring})
AND browser_family IN (${browsers:sqlstring})
AND referrer_domain IN (${referrals:sqlstring})
AND country_code IN (${locations:sqlstring})

SELECT $__timeInterval(timestamp) as time, COUNT(DISTINCT(visitor_id)) * ${sample}
FROM "prisme"."events_pageviews"
SAMPLE 1/${sample}
WHERE $__timeFilter(timestamp)
AND domain IN (${domains:sqlstring})
AND path IN (${pathnames:sqlstring})
AND operating_system IN (${operating_systems:sqlstring})
AND browser_family IN (${browsers:sqlstring})
AND referrer_domain IN (${referrals:sqlstring})
AND referrer_domain != domain
AND country_code IN (${locations:sqlstring})
GROUP BY time
ORDER BY time

targets.rawSql:
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT(visitor_id)) * ${sample} AS "Live visitors"
FROM prisme.events_pageviews
SAMPLE 1/${sample}
WHERE timestamp > subtractMinutes(now(), 15)
AND domain IN (${domains:sqlstring})
AND path IN (${pathnames:sqlstring})
AND operating_system IN (${operating_systems:sqlstring})
AND browser_family IN (${browsers:sqlstring})
AND referrer_domain IN (${referrals:sqlstring})
AND country_code IN (${locations:sqlstring})

WITH visitor_visits AS (
  SELECT visitor_id, COUNT(*) AS "visits"
  FROM prisme.events_pageviews
  WHERE $__timeFilter(timestamp)
  AND domain IN (${domains:sqlstring})
  AND path IN (${pathnames:sqlstring})
  AND operating_system IN (${operating_systems:sqlstring})
  AND browser_family IN (${browsers:sqlstring})
  AND referrer_domain IN (${referrals:sqlstring})
  AND country_code IN (${locations:sqlstring})
  GROUP BY visitor_id
)
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM visitor_visits WHERE visits = 1

panels.title: Time Series

targets.rawSql:
SELECT referrer_domain, COUNT(*) as count
FROM "prisme"."events_pageviews"
WHERE $__timeFilter(timestamp)
AND domain IN (${domains:sqlstring})
AND path IN (${pathnames:sqlstring})
AND operating_system IN (${operating_systems:sqlstring})
AND browser_family IN (${browsers:sqlstring})
AND referrer_domain IN (${referrals:sqlstring})
AND country_code IN (${locations:sqlstring})
GROUP BY referrer_domain
ORDER BY count DESC

SELECT COUNT() AS Internal
FROM "prisme"."events_pageviews"
WHERE $__timeFilter(timestamp)
AND domain IN (${domains:sqlstring})
AND path IN (${pathnames:sqlstring})
AND operating_system IN (${operating_systems:sqlstring})
AND browser_family IN (${browsers:sqlstring})
AND referrer_domain IN (${referrals:sqlstring})
AND referrer_domain = domain
AND country_code IN (${locations:sqlstring})

SELECT COUNT(*) AS Direct
FROM "prisme"."events_pageviews"
WHERE $__timeFilter(timestamp)
AND domain IN (${domains:sqlstring})
AND path IN (${pathnames:sqlstring})
AND operating_system IN (${operating_systems:sqlstring})
AND browser_family IN (${browsers:sqlstring})
AND referrer_domain IN (${referrals:sqlstring})
AND referrer_domain = 'direct'
AND country_code IN (${locations:sqlstring})

SELECT COUNT(*) AS External
FROM "prisme"."events_pageviews"
WHERE $__timeFilter(timestamp)
AND domain IN (${domains:sqlstring})
AND path IN (${pathnames:sqlstring})
AND operating_system IN (${operating_systems:sqlstring})
AND browser_family IN (${browsers:sqlstring})
AND referrer_domain IN (${referrals:sqlstring})
AND referrer_domain != 'direct' AND referrer_domain != domain
AND country_code IN (${locations:sqlstring})

SELECT path, COUNT(*) as pageviews
FROM "prisme"."events_pageviews"
WHERE $__timeFilter(timestamp)
AND domain IN (${domains:sqlstring})
AND path IN (${pathnames:sqlstring})
AND operating_system IN (${operating_systems:sqlstring})
AND browser_family IN (${browsers:sqlstring})
AND referrer_domain IN (${referrals:sqlstring})
AND country_code IN (${locations:sqlstring})
GROUP BY path
ORDER BY pageviews DESC

SELECT country_code, COUNT(*) as pageview
FROM "prisme"."events_pageviews"
WHERE $__timeFilter(timestamp)
AND domain IN (${domains:sqlstring})
AND path IN (${pathnames:sqlstring})
AND operating_system IN (${operating_systems:sqlstring})
AND browser_family IN (${browsers:sqlstring})
AND referrer_domain IN (${referrals:sqlstring})
AND country_code IN (${locations:sqlstring})
GROUP BY country_code
ORDER BY country_code

SELECT DISTINCT(name) AS country, COUNT(*) as pageview
FROM prisme.events_pageviews
JOIN prisme.countries ON prisme.events_pageviews.country_code = prisme.countries.code
WHERE $__timeFilter(timestamp)
AND domain IN (${domains:sqlstring})
AND path IN (${pathnames:sqlstring})
AND operating_system IN (${operating_systems:sqlstring})
AND browser_family IN (${browsers:sqlstring})
AND referrer_domain IN (${referrals:sqlstring})
AND country_code IN (${locations:sqlstring})
GROUP BY country
ORDER BY pageview DESC

SELECT replaceRegexpAll(browser_family, '(.*) (Mobile|iOS)|Mobile (.*)', '\\1\\2') AS browser_family, COUNT(browser_family) as count
FROM "prisme"."events_pageviews"
WHERE $__timeFilter(timestamp)
AND domain IN (${domains:sqlstring})
AND path IN (${pathnames:sqlstring})
AND operating_system IN (${operating_systems:sqlstring})
AND browser_family IN (${browsers:sqlstring})
AND referrer_domain IN (${referrals:sqlstring})
AND country_code IN (${locations:sqlstring})
GROUP BY browser_family

SELECT operating_system, COUNT(operating_system) as count
FROM "prisme"."events_pageviews"
WHERE $__timeFilter(timestamp)
AND domain IN (${domains:sqlstring})
AND path IN (${pathnames:sqlstring})
AND operating_system IN (${operating_systems:sqlstring})
AND browser_family IN (${browsers:sqlstring})
AND referrer_domain IN (${referrals:sqlstring})
AND country_code IN (${locations:sqlstring})
GROUP BY operating_system

SELECT name, COUNT(*) as count
FROM "prisme"."events_custom"
WHERE $__timeFilter(timestamp)
AND domain IN (${domains:sqlstring})
AND path IN (${pathnames:sqlstring})
AND operating_system IN (${operating_systems:sqlstring})
AND browser_family IN (${browsers:sqlstring})
AND referrer_domain IN (${referrals:sqlstring})
AND country_code IN (${locations:sqlstring})
GROUP BY name
ORDER BY count DESC
